{"tid":2041430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部：若英予香港居民永久居留，中方保留反制權利","createTime":"2020-05-29T08:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T14:22:03.000Z","uid":278587,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3b947997b171a53d4c0f70f929787e7d5a4732","tid":2041430,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200525/s00001/cb0f0241f8561d23258bb21ef60fc70b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200525%2Fs00001%2Fcb0f0241f8561d23258bb21ef60fc70b.jpg&h=02fb0b66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】在北京，外交部說如果英國給予香港居民永久居留權，中方保留對英國採取反制措施的權利。<br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文較早前說，如果中國實施港區國安法，英方會延長英國國民（海外）護照，即BNO持有人的逗留期限，由免簽證入境六個月，改為容許護照持有人在英國工作及學習十二個月，長遠可以作為進一步申請公民資格的途徑。<br />\n<br />\n有關注香港事務的保守黨國會議員指，藍韜文的聲明是個好開始，但期望當局採取更多措施，包括加快BNO持有人取得英國公民資格的程序。<br />\n<br />\n在野自由民主黨則呼籲當局，將BNO持有人的權利延伸至所有香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392659&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33HXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=3acfd08d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392659&h=10e07fae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392659</a>"},{"pid":"e5b699d0dd957e5ec195650935052b2ae819c409","tid":2041430,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"but how"},{"pid":"3c00458dc7590ea32e48e34de82e7f9d06a5f88f","tid":2041430,"uid":277659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:36:34.000Z","msg":"口交部"},{"pid":"63a93f7f76cddf486d562d21121c05d7b3f05a07","tid":2041430,"uid":57088,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:37:11.000Z","msg":"英國收哂你啲眼中釘，點解咁唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"